INSERT INTO `blogs` (`title`, `slug`, `content`, `category`, `tags`, `tag_slug`, `images`, `poststatus`, `datecreated`, `createdby`, `id`) VALUES
('Top 10 Best Locations to Buy an Independent House in South Chennai', 'top-10-best-locations-to-buy-an-independent-house-in-south-chennai', '<p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Introduction</strong></p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">&nbsp;</strong>So you’ve decided to invest in your own house, have you? Excellent decision. Owning your place is incredibly rewarding. If you want to<span>&nbsp;</span><em>sell your house</em>, you can do that as well.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">But house hunting in a big city like Chennai can feel overwhelming and a<span>&nbsp;</span><em>house sale in Chennai<span>&nbsp;</span></em>can be daunting. Where do you even start? Don’t worry, we’ve got you covered!</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">We spent weeks researching the best neighborhoods in South Chennai to&nbsp; find independent houses with solid infrastructure, access to amenities, and room for growth. Why South Chennai? This part of the city has seen massive development in individual houses for sale in Chennai in recent years, with new roads, metro lines, schools, hospitals and more.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Property values are going up, up, up, ensuring you get the<em><span>&nbsp;</span>best house</em>. Get in now while you still have a chance at a good deal. In this list, we’re highlighting the top 10 locations we think are the absolute best for finding an independent house as well as a<span>&nbsp;</span><em>villa for sale in Chennai</em><span>&nbsp;</span>which you’ll be proud to call home. Ready to take a tour of the hottest housing markets in South Chennai? Let’s dive right in!</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Adyar – A Prime Residential Hub in South Chennai</strong></p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">It is one of the most sought-after residential localities in South Chennai, and for good reason. This leafy neighborhood along the Adyar River is perfect for those looking to escape.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Tranquil surroundings</strong></p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em>Buying a house<span>&nbsp;</span></em>in a peaceful environment, surrounded by greenery is ideal if you want to unwind after a long day. Take a stroll along the Theosophical Society Gardens or simply sit by the river and relax. The chirping of birds and rustling of leaves are the only sounds you’ll hear.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Well-connected yet serene</strong></p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Despite its calm setting, it remains well-linked to the rest of Chennai. It lies along the arterial Gandhi Mandapam Road and Kamaraj Avenue, providing easy access to other parts of the city. You get the best of both worlds – a quiet home nestled amid nature as well as convenience to travel wherever you need to go.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Cultural hubs and entertainment options</strong></p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Adyar</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>also boasts many spots for pursuing hobbies and leisure activities. Visit the Foundation to experience traditional Tamil arts or catch the latest plays at Ranga Shankara. When you want to dine out or go shopping, Market and Khader Nawaz Khan Road have you covered.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">With premium amenities, connectivity, and a perfect environment for recreation and rejuvenation, Aglyan makes an outstanding choice if you’re looking to purchase an<em><span>&nbsp;</span>independent house for sale in Chennai.</em><span>&nbsp;</span>The residential properties here let you live comfortably while enjoying a lifestyle of peace and cultural enrichment.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Besant Nagar –</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>A Beachfront Neighborhood Near IT Corridor</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">If you’re looking to<em><span>&nbsp;</span>buy a home</em><span>&nbsp;</span>near the IT hub but also want to enjoy a beachfront lifestyle, Besant Nagar should be at the top of your list.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nestled between the bustling IT corridor and scenic Elliots Beach, Besant Nagar gives you the best of both worlds. The tree-lined streets and colonial-style houses offer a quiet respite from city life, yet the neighborhood remains well-connected to the rest of Chennai.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">You’ll find everything you need within walking distance -restaurants, shops, schools, and entertainment. Take an evening stroll down the beach promenade, watch the sunset over the Bay of Bengal, and grab dinner at one of the beach shacks. For the active type, there’s a walking/jogging track, and swimming pools.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Property values here have steadily increased over the years, but you can still find independent houses under ₹10 crore. Look for houses on streets like 1st, 2nd and 3rd Avenues, as well as B.P. Ajith Kumar Road.<span>&nbsp;</span><em>Buying properties</em><span>&nbsp;</span>in these locations puts you closest to the beach while still keeping you connected to the main road network.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">If a sea-facing villa is out of your budget, houses a few streets back from the beachfront can save you a sizable amount while still giving you easy access to Besant Nagar’s many attractions. With its vibrant yet laid-back lifestyle and proximity to major employers, Besant Nagar offers the ideal live-work balance for homebuyers in South Chennai.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Thiruvanmiyur-</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>Combining Suburban Living With Urban Convenience</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">If you want the best of both worlds, this is an ideal location to consider for your new home. Chennai properties in this area have a quiet, laid-back vibe but are only a 15- minute drive from the hustle and bustle of the city center.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Living in Thiruvanmiyur you’ll enjoy a peaceful environment surrounded by lush greenery and parks, with the Bay of Bengal just a stone’s throw away. At the same time, all the conveniences of city life are right at your doorstep. Shopping centers, restaurants, schools, and hospitals are easily accessible. You’ll never feel too far from the action.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Connectivity is another major plus in<span>&nbsp;</span><em>Chennai houses<span>&nbsp;</span></em>in Thiruvanmiyur&nbsp; is situated along the East Coast Road, making it simple to get into the city or head out to scenic beach towns as several bus routes also serve the area, and the Velachery railway station is just 5 kilometers away.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Due to the suburb’s many desirable qualities, property prices in Thiruvanmiyur have been steadily rising over the years. However, you can still find good value homes here compared to more central city locations. Look for apartments, villas or plot lands to build your dream house. If a peaceful environment, great connectivity and convenience are what you’re after in your property search, buying a<span>&nbsp;</span><em>house in Chennai</em>, especially in</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">deserves to be high on your list. This charming suburb has all the ingredients for a high quality of life at a relatively affordable cost. Check it out—you may just find your perfect new home.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Velachery –</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>A Fast-Developing Suburb With Connectivity</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Velachery is a fast-developing suburb in South Chennai with excellent connectivity. Located just 15 km from the Chennai International Airport and 7 km from the Chennai Central Railway Station, Velachery provides hassle-free transit options.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The Mass Rapid Transit System (MRTS) and suburban trains facilitate smooth travel within the city. Several bus services operated by the Metropolitan Transport Corporation (MTC) connect Velachery to other parts of Chennai. The proposed Phase II metro rail expansion also includes Velachery.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Velachery is home to many IT companies like Cognizant Technology Solutions, Wipro Limited, and Tata Consultancy Services. The availability of commercial office spaces, proximity to IT hubs like OMR and Guindy, and connectivity have attracted many IT and ITES companies to Velachery. The presence of these companies has led to an increase in demand for residential properties in Velachery.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">You’ll find apartments, flats, and villas of various sizes in Velachery to suit different budgets.&nbsp; 2 BHK and 3 BHK are popular options for small to mid-sized families. The capital and rental values here are relatively lower compared to other suburbs of Chennai. The amenities include supermarkets, schools, colleges, hospitals, restaurants, banks, and entertainment options.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The nearby Guindy National Park and the serene backwaters of Chembarambakkam Lake offer opportunities for outdoor activities. The pristine beach is just 30 km from here.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">With many infrastructure projects in the pipeline, Velachery is poised to become one of the most sought-after residential destinations in Chennai. For those looking to buy an independent house as well as an<span>&nbsp;</span><em>individual villa for sale in Chennai</em>, Velachery should be high on your list. Its strategic location, connectivity, presence of amenities, natural surroundings, and&nbsp; proximity to IT hubs make it an ideal choice for a house in South Chennai.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Perumbakkam-</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>An Affordable Emerging Residential Location</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Perumbakkam is an up-and-coming residential area located in South Chennai that offers affordable housing options and<span>&nbsp;</span><em>independent villas for sale in Chennai.</em><span>&nbsp;</span>Located just 30 minutes from major employment hubs like OMR and GST Road, Perumbakkam central location and lower costs of living make it an attractive suburb for young families and Professionals.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Infrastructure and Connectivity</strong></p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">&nbsp;</strong>Well connected by road and rail, has seen major infrastructure improvements in recent years. The Perumbakkam bus terminus provides connectivity to various parts of Chennai. The Perumbakkam Railway Station on the Chengalpattu-Chennai Beach suburban railway line makes it</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">easy to travel into the city for work or leisure. The Chennai Metro’s Phase 2 expansion plans include a station at which will further increase connectivity.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\">Lower Cost of Living</strong></p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Housing and living costs in Perumbakkam are relatively lower compared to other parts of Chennai due to the availability of land and lower property prices. You can find 2 and 3 BHK apartments within a budget of up to 70 lakhs. Rental options are also affordable, ranging from to 15,000 per month for a 2 BHK home.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overall, if you’re looking to<span>&nbsp;</span><em>buy an apartment in Chennai<span>&nbsp;</span></em>with good connectivity in South Chennai, Perumbakkam is worth considering. Proximity to employment hubs, availability of amenities, and planned infrastructure upgrades make it an attractive suburb for young homebuyers. Act fast before property prices start rising due to increasing demand and new developments in this destination.</p><h3 style=\" margin-block: 0.5rem 1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.75rem; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Conclusion</h3><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">You’ve now seen some of the best spots in South Chennai to consider<em><span>&nbsp;</span>buying real estate</em>. Whether you want an affordable<span>&nbsp;</span><em>individual house in Chennai<span>&nbsp;</span></em>or i<em>ndividual villas in Chennai</em>, this part of the city has options for every budget and lifestyle.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The neighborhoods here have a perfect blend of city living and natural surroundings. Now that you’ve explored the possibilities, it’s time to start viewing some properties and negotiating with<span>&nbsp;</span><em>individual house builders in Chennai.</em></p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Before you know it, you could be moving into your little slice of paradise in South Chennai. The independence and security of owning your own home awaits! All you have to do is take that first step.</p>\r\n<br /></p>', '', 'Perumbakkam,Lower Cost of Living', 'perumbakkam,lower-cost-of-living', 'aa06b96444f9fbbdf70ea6444f2ade59.jpg', 'active', '1706164189000', '67564534', 3);
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`title`, `slug`, `content`, `category`, `tags`, `tag_slug`, `images`, `poststatus`, `datecreated`, `createdby`, `id`) VALUES
('7 long-Run Benefits of Buying a Flat in Chennai in 2023 for Your Family', '7-long-run-benefits-of-buying-a-flat-in-chennai-in-2023-for-your-family', '<p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">So you’re thinking of investing in some property in Chennai to secure your family’s future. Smart thinking! While the stock market can be volatile, real estate values in major Indian cities like Chennai have steadily climbed over the decades. And buying a flat offers stability and security for your loved ones that’s hard to beat.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Buying<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\"><em>flats for sale in Chennai<span>&nbsp;</span></em></strong>is relatively easier as you can skim through a lot of websites and choose the ones you like, but a detailed overview and the emotional ties need to be addressed as well.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Chennai, the capital city of Tamil Nadu, is one of the fastest-growing metropolitan cities in India. It is a hub for various industries, including IT, automobile, and manufacturing. The city has a rich cultural heritage and is known for its beautiful beaches, temples, and historical monuments. With ever growing need, there’s always an option to invest in cities that yield better returns.<strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\"><em><span>&nbsp;</span>Houses for sale in Chennai<span>&nbsp;</span></em></strong>is also a great place to invest in real estate, and buying a flat in Chennai in 2023 can be a wise decision for your family.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Not convinced yet? Here are seven reasons why purchasing<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\"><em>apartments for sale<span>&nbsp;</span></em></strong><strong style=\" font-weight: bolder\"><em>in Chennai</em></strong><span>&nbsp;</span>and why it might just be one of the savviest financial decisions you’ll ever make for your family. From near­ guaranteed appreciation and rental income to stability and community, the benefits of having flat ownership in this cultural capital of South India are manifold.</p><p style=\" margin-block: 0px 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Ready to ensure your family’s well-being for generations to come? Then check out why Chennai flat is calling your